description:
Both Welterweights and both with a lifetime record of 1-0. The Pirates victory was over Jenni Lee and Xana's victory over the Dragon. Xana is the clear contender in that weight category, or have we all underestimated the Pirate? The final score was 79-58. The second closest match in US history. Who got fucked by who?
Corine scorekeeper
title: The Pirate (0-0) vs. Xana Star (0-0)
